This is a simple frame for PHP

PHP Version - 5.3+



//Constants

WHERE_AM_I - to define where the program runs. possible values are local and online

Developer Safe Mode - http://192.168.0.8/PHPFrame/developer/?safemode=true

Model class will be - "class configModel extends modelclass"

execute action function argument changed to array

siteclass::addHook(array("fromClass"=>"configModel","fromFunction"=>"GetFooter","toClass"=>"siteclass","toFunction"=>"testHook"));

